name: ImportHS6e
description:
# HeroSystem6e api script
This API is designed for use with the [HeroSystem6e character sheet](https://github.com/Roll20/roll20-character-sheets/tree/master/HeroSystem6e) and the [HeroSystem6e api].  If you are not using those, this api script will most likely be of no use to you.

This api script imports character sheets from the gmnotes field on that character sheet.
